title: Lethal Cold
tooltip: universal property: extreme cold, creatures become resistant to fire
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While on a [[plane]] with this property, creatures are subjected to extreme cold. In addition, all creatures gain resistance to [[fire damage|damage type]], and a creature that is usually resistant to fire damage becomes immune to it.